s affect them.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/48906/', '', 'Minoxidil, Deoxycholic acid, Calcium gluconate, Pimecrolimus, Magnesium sulfate, Aminobenzoic acid, Finasteride, Ivermectin, Caffeine, Diclofenac, Cromoglicic acid, More', 'Citalopram, Duloxetine, Vilazodone, Sertraline, Paroxetine, Desvenlafaxine, Fluoxetine, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, More', 1767369485);
